description:
Step into a world where vibrant street art meets exquisite cuisine. This London restaurant, located on the iconic Brick Lane, features a stunning mural of a bejeweled woman with sunglasses, a tribute to modern Indian art. The interior blends bold, colorful murals with elegant decor, creating the perfect setting to enjoy delicious street food and creative cocktails. This is more than just a meal; it's a feast for the senses, capturing the unique spirit of East London's dynamic food and art scene.

@Bahara restaurant: 79 Brick Ln, London E1
Artist unknown.
